title: Eric Clapton & Friends - The Album (2015) [FLAC]
description:
A low price compilation including EC's early works with The Yardbirds (CD1) and other cooperations (CD2) - varying audio quality & unfortunately without adequate liner notes - for example tracks 43 & 44 are uncredited Howlin' Wolf recordings. BTW: The CD release tracklist differs from the tracklist of this web release
